  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bb0 \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Emergency circular issued",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Public Administration has sent a circular to the heads of state-owned enterprises to invite minimum and essential staff for daily services until further notice."
      ],
